**Internet Redundancy:** GL.iNet GL-MT6000 Router (dual-WAN failover) · Netgear Nighthawk M7 Pro 5G (backup) · Bingfu MIMO Antenna · USB-C Ethernet Adapter · Speedify (bonding/failover software)

**Power Backup:** Anker 737 24,000mAh (laptop) · TalentCell Mini UPS (router) · ELECOM NESTOUT 15,000mAh (emergency)

**Charging:** Anker 100W 3-Port GaN · Anker 7-in-1 USB-C Hub · Anker Prime 240W Cable

