**Uptime Target:** 99.9% — wired primary + 5G failover + Speedify bonding + battery backup on laptop and router. But the target is not dependent on everything working. The floor is: laptop + webcam + mic + 10 Mbps upload on ethernet = reliable stream. The redundancy layers raise the ceiling. They don't hold up the floor.

